00:42:05.295 --> 00:42:20.529
One last call, one last push for a major move of God. I thank you for the underground churches in Asia; they will rise up and be bolder than they've ever been.

00:42:20.530 --> 00:42:36.651
A supernatural anointing will rest upon them. The Shekinah glory cloud.

00:42:36.652 --> 00:42:50.859
People having arms and legs and eyes and ears replaced. Nothing missing, nothing broken.

00:42:50.860 --> 00:43:03.830
We call forth a great harvest of souls. People leaving Buddha and leaving Muhammad and all the false religions.

00:43:03.831 --> 00:43:25.691
A great move of God in Russia, over Moscow and over all the cities. A supernatural fire will move over the land.

00:43:25.692 --> 00:43:36.879
All over Africa, from the north to the south, there will be a great harvest of souls.

00:43:36.880 --> 00:43:50.273
We call forth a great harvest throughout South America and Australia—a radical visitation for the fire of God over Queensland.

00:43:50.274 --> 00:44:06.785
We give you great glory for a mighty move over all the islands, from Jamaica to the Philippines.

00:44:06.786 --> 00:44:13.453
One last push, for the time of your Son is coming; he is standing at the door.

00:44:13.454 --> 00:44:28.463
We thank you, Lord, for a financial victory and manifestations of money to support your gospel throughout the whole world, not to hoard it but to be a blessing.

00:44:28.464 --> 00:44:46.753
We give you all the glory for it and consider it done. We thank you, Lord, that you're moving in Hollywood.

00:44:46.754 --> 00:44:58.974
There will be a move in the celebrities; they will turn from their wicked ways.

00:44:58.975 --> 00:45:10.717
They are hungry and thirsty and they will find it not in New Age or Satanism or the occult, but they will find it in you.

00:45:10.718 --> 00:45:44.114
A new river of living water will flow over Hollywood. We thank you, Lord, that there's one last call for a great harvest.

00:45:44.115 --> 00:45:52.270
The harvesters are here now, rising up with great boldness to bring in the lost.

00:45:52.271 --> 00:46:27.838
I feel his presence. Thank you, Father, for moving in the midst of these people.

00:46:27.839 --> 00:46:35.756
Moving upon Mexico, Guatemala, El Salvador, and Venezuela.

00:46:35.757 --> 00:47:01.603
We call for a revival, Lord! One last call for a great harvest of souls.

00:47:01.604 --> 00:47:14.837
Let the church bells ring and let the people wake up, for Jesus Christ is coming again.

00:47:14.838 --> 00:47:40.012
It's time to wake up. Breathe on the people today, Holy Spirit, in their houses and in their cars.

00:47:40.013 --> 00:47:48.109
We call for fresh fire and a fresh touch of the living water. Fresh fire in Jesus'name!

00:47:48.110 --> 00:48:49.134
Shake them once again, Lord! New wine and a new wineskin over them right now.

00:48:49.135 --> 00:49:17.137
Holy Spirit, we call for revival in the Jewish community. A flood of your salvation will flow over the Jewish community.

00:49:17.138 --> 00:49:28.553
We thank you, Lord, that you're real to them, just like you were to the children of Israel.

00:49:28.555 --> 00:49:48.234
Great demonstrations throughout Israel; appear to them, Father, as the Messiah Jesus Christ has come in the flesh.

00:49:48.235 --> 00:50:17.002
A harvest coming all throughout Canada, throughout Quebec and British Columbia. A great move like they've never seen before.

00:50:17.003 --> 00:52:03.598
Over Ireland, we call forth a revival in Jesus'name, and over the UK, Iceland, Finland, and Nova Scotia.

00:52:03.599 --> 00:52:29.033
A revival that is moving all over South America, all throughout the Amazon River. We call for those people to be born again.

00:52:29.034 --> 00:53:02.109
From the top of the Amazon all the way down, we call for a move of the spirit of the Lord. Lord, they will not be able to stand and hide anymore.

00:53:02.110 --> 00:53:17.439
There's great witchcraft over that area, but at the rising of the sun, the people will be free.

00:53:17.440 --> 00:54:14.676
Jesus will be made known. He is alive and arose again. He has come to set the captives free.

00:54:14.677 --> 00:54:49.946
All over the Middle East—in Jordan, Iraq, Oman, and Yemen, Afghanistan, Turkey—we call for revival in Jesus'name.

00:54:49.947 --> 00:55:58.679
Rising like a mighty wave! A revival like a blanket over the southern border.

00:55:58.680 --> 00:56:09.811
The sun is setting for this dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:56:09.812 --> 00:56:32.038
Jesus is standing at the door. We're out of time. He's given us a four-year window.

00:56:32.039 --> 00:56:58.181
There's a four-year time of the Shemitah cycle. I see a light in every single year and it's getting brighter and brighter.

00:56:58.182 --> 00:57:39.130
The glory! We should be focused on the glory. The popcorn kernels are popping.

00:57:39.131 --> 00:58:18.038
The enemy thinks he has won, but there is a great harvest yet to come.

00:58:18.039 --> 00:58:36.492
It's like an orchestra, a beautiful orchestra flowing, moving in the spirit.

00:58:36.493 --> 00:58:49.891
As people get born again, they're adding to the orchestra. It's expanding.

00:58:49.892 --> 00:59:01.125
New believers are bringing more people in. The music is playing before the Father.

00:59:01.126 --> 00:59:26.941
I see the Hallelujah ringing. The people are moving together as an army and then we all go up.

00:59:26.942 --> 00:59:50.900
We're singing Hallelujah before the Father. We're moving as an orchestra, a beautiful symphony.

00:59:50.901 --> 01:01:37.679
New notes are coming up like rainbows out of the people. We praise and we adore thee, bowing down before thee, oh Lord.

01:01:37.680 --> 01:01:45.119
I see them all marching together; they blended as one. All those people I saw being added during the revival kept growing and expanding.

01:01:45.120 --> 01:01:51.629
They were singing and making melody to the Lord. Then all of a sudden they were caught up in the Rapture.

01:01:51.630 --> 01:01:55.349
They were sitting before his throne and they all became one fire.

01:01:55.350 --> 01:01:59.999
It was beautiful blue fire that went before the Father. He was breathing it in.

01:02:00.000 --> 01:02:05.889
Those people were gathering up their friends and family, and the glory was bringing them in as a harvest.

01:02:05.890 --> 01:02:11.469
Each person was golden and shining with glory. Then we all got sucked up like shafts of light.

01:02:11.470 --> 01:02:13.119
All of it became one. All those individuals became one body before the Father, and the fire came.

01:02:13.120 --> 01:02:13.319
Hallelujah is ringing from every tribe and every tongue. They're all coming to the Son.

01:02:13.320 --> 01:06:27.038
We praise and we adore thee, bowing down before thee. My goodness, babe, I look forward to it so much.

01:06:27.039 --> 01:07:18.916
He's given us a window. I assure you time is running out. Stay on the vine.

01:07:18.917 --> 01:09:04.559
Jesus is coming. Days of heaven on earth. We thank you for the harvest, for you're the Lord of the harvest.

01:09:04.560 --> 01:09:24.508
He is the storehouse. Well, we're excited you joined us today.

01:09:24.509 --> 01:09:43.814
We pray this prayer time has blessed you today. For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:09:43.815 --> 01:10:18.363
Will you help him bring in the harvest today? Thank you for praying with us. You truly are family to us. Jesus is coming!

01:10:18.364 --> 01:10:32.122
We're excited to raise up a million people to pray with us on a day-to-day basis for a time of refreshing.

01:10:32.123 --> 01:10:56.319
He said it's time for my body to be refreshed. Allow him to flow like he just did.

01:10:56.320 --> 01:12:09.235
No agenda other than just to give him glory. To bring and assemble that body together to worship and magnify the King. Fresh fire! When it's like this, I don't want to let it go.

01:12:09.236 --> 01:13:47.863
In the presence of Jehovah, God Almighty, Prince of Peace, troubles vanish, hearts are mended, in the presence of the King.

01:13:47.864 --> 01:15:01.231
There's a wave of healing that just hit right then. Receive what you're believing for today.

01:15:01.232 --> 01:15:39.331
Restoration is happening for you today. He is holy. Lord, there is none like you.

01:15:39.332 --> 01:16:16.942
I sing your praises forever. Deeper in love with you, Jesus.

01:16:16.943 --> 01:17:00.609
There's just something about your name. Master, Savior, Jesus, like a fragrance after the rain.

01:17:00.610 --> 01:17:49.491
Let all heaven and earth proclaim: kings and kingdoms will all pass away, but there's something about your name.

01:17:49.492 --> 01:18:08.073
Well, praise the Lord. Diana, I really don't know how to end other than saying we love you.

01:18:08.074 --> 01:18:22.931
God bless you all. Remember: put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you, and we love you.

01:18:22.932 --> 01:18:40.093
We pray the presence of the Lord comes into your house like he is in ours right now.

01:18:40.094 --> 01:18:55.839
If you practice his presence, he will come. Well, we will see you again tomorrow.

01:18:55.840 --> 01:19:05.230
We are blessed by every day we get to come. This blessed me as much as it blessed you.

01:19:05.231 --> 01:19:27.918
I look forward to these times. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart and we will see you tomorrow. God bless you all. Have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

